    Add HTTP/SSE Server for Web Integration
    Adds server-sse.ts implementing MCP Streamable HTTP transport for web services and browser clients.
    Key Changes:
    New Express-based HTTP server with SSE support
    Session management with Bearer token authentication
    CORS enabled, health check endpoint at /health
    Default to read-only mode for security (both stdio and SSE)
    Added express, @types/express, tsx dependencies
    New scripts: npm run dev:sse and npm run start:sse
    Usage:
    SHORTCUT_API_TOKEN=your_token npm run dev:sse# Add SHORTCUT_READONLY=false for write access
    The existing stdio server remains unchanged.

