    Add comprehensive external links management for Shortcut stories
    
    This commit implements complete external link management functionality
    for Shortcut stories through four new MCP tools and supporting client methods.
    
    Features added:
    - Add external links to stories with duplicate prevention
    - Remove specific external links from stories
    - Search for stories containing specific external links
    - Bulk replace all external links on a story
    
    New MCP tools:
    - add-external-link-to-story: Add single external link
    - remove-external-link-from-story: Remove specific external link
    - get-stories-by-external-link: Find stories by external link
    - set-story-external-links: Replace all external links (bulk operation)
    
    Technical details:
    - 4 new client methods in ShortcutClientWrapper
    - Full URL validation with 2048 character limit
    - Comprehensive test coverage (47 tests total)
    - Follows existing codebase patterns and conventions
    - Proper error handling and response formatting
    
